OL,7,FA husband has said he has been left
OL,8,Fperforming a medical procedure on his
OL,9,Fwife after doctors failed to offer her
OL,10,Fan operation sooner.
OL,12,FLinda Henderson, 69, has been living
OL,13,Fwith Parkinson's for more than a
OL,14,Fdecade, and asthma all her life. But
OL,15,Fshe said that the prolapsed womb she
OL,16,Fhas had since 2018 has left her
OL,17,Fstruggling to leave the house.
