OL,7,FIt was her birthday on Monday and it
OL,8,Fwas the first time she has been unable
OL,9,Fto go out to celebrate it, as the
OL,10,Fprolapse means she cannot walk far.
OL,12,FShe told ITV Central: "The way I put
OL,13,Fit is it's not much of a life now,
OL,14,Feverything is just revolving around
OL,15,Fthis."
