OL,4,Cprocedure on wife who wasn't 'offered
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,FHe said: 'What do you do? You're
OL,8,Fpresented with a situation, you can
OL,9,Feither go one or two ways. I can
OL,10,Feither pick up the phone and call 999
OL,11,Fand four hours later an ambulance
OL,12,Fmight come.
OL,14,F"We did do that on one occasion, we
OL,15,Fcalled 111 and it was a waste of time
OL,16,Fas 4 hours down the line an ambulance
OL,17,Fdidn't come.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
