OL,3,CHusband left performing medical
OL,4,Cprocedure on wife who wasn't 'offered
OL,5,Coperation'
OL,7,F"So I just carried on as best as I
OL,8,Fcould and that's what I've been doing
OL,9,Fdaily/weekly/ three or four times a
OL,10,Fweek since. And it is wrong, I could
OL,11,Fhave caused Linda some serious
OL,12,Fproblems."
OL,14,FLinda is now due to have a
OL,15,Fhysterectomy soon. It was meant to be
OL,16,Fnext week, but they have been told
OL,17,Ftoday it is being delayed until April
OL,18,Fbecause of a lack of ICU bed
OL,19,Favailable. That is needed because
OL,20,FLinda's conditions make her at high
OL,21,Frisk.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
