OL,7,FThe local trust that Linda is
OL,8,Fcurrently receiving care from, Walsall
OL,9,FHealthcare NHS Trust, has told ITV
OL,10,FCentral: "We understand it's
OL,11,Ffrustrating for Mrs Henderson and
OL,12,Fother patients when surgery cannot go
OL,13,Fahead as planned.
OL,15,F"A new date has been scheduled for her
OL,16,Fsurgery."
